<h2>About Me</h2>
<p>I am a <b>2nd year PhD student</b> in <a href="http://wncg.org/">Wireless Networking and Communication Group (WNCG)</a>, <a href="http://www.utexas.edu">UT Austin</a>. I am currently advised by <a href="http://users.ece.utexas.edu/~nikolova/">Prof. Evdokia Nikolova</a> and co-advised by <a href="http://users.ece.utexas.edu/~shakkott////Sanjay_Shakkottai/Contact.html">Prof. Sanjay Shakkottai</a>. Earlier during my undergraduate studies I have wroked under <a href="http://www.ecdept.iitkgp.ernet.in/index.php/home/faculty/gdas">Prof. Goutam Das</a> in <a href="http://www.iitkgp.ac.in">IIT Kharagpur</a>. Here is my <a href="cv/CV_Soumya_Basu.pdf">CV</a>. </p> 

<p>I am interested in empolying concepts from <b>Advanced Probability</b>, <b>Algorithimic Game Thoery</b> &amp; <b>Optimization Theory </b> in Design of Scalable Algorithms with provable guarantees. Problems in <b>Stochastic Networks</b> and <b>Machine Learning</b>, with real world apllications, align to my core interests and steer my <a href="research.html">research</a>. </p>


</td></tr></table>



